1.title: Trouble in Paradise

episode of.title: Kourtney & Khloé Take the Hamptons (TV Series 2014–2015)

1.plot: When Kourtney, Khloé, and Scott arrive in the Hamptons to start their picture-perfect summer, Scott is overwhelmed by the anxiety of being in his late parents' hometown and runs back to his old habits. Meanwhile, Khloé jets off on a romantic getaway to South Africa with her new boyfriend, French Montana.

2.title: What's That Racquet?

episode of.title: Kourtney & Khloé Take the Hamptons (TV Series 2014–2015)

2.plot: After Kourtney admonishes Scott for breaking the boundaries they've set for their relationship, Scott makes attempts to clean up his act and get back in her good graces. Meanwhile, Khloé tries to get Scott on a healthy track with tennis, but her good deed backfires when Kourtney accuses her of taking Scott's side.

3.title: Party Crashing

episode of.title: Kourtney & Khloé Take the Hamptons (TV Series 2014–2015)

3.plot: When Kourtney learns that Kim is using her home for North's birthday party without her permission, she flies to LA to confront her. Meanwhile, back in the Hamptons, Scott finds himself in the hospital after partying too much and realizes he must make a change.

4.title: 12 Steps and 30 Candles

episode of.title: Kourtney & Khloé Take the Hamptons (TV Series 2014–2015)

4.plot: Scott decides to go to rehab, but is quick to change his mind. Khloe has to accept that her life is gone the opposite of how she planned it.

5.title: Aftershocks

episode of.title: Kourtney & Khloé Take the Hamptons (TV Series 2014–2015)

5.plot: Kourtney and Scott must come to terms when Scott crosses rehab off the list. Kim doubts trusting Jonathan after the tabloids claim secrets that only Kim told Jonathan.

6.title: Kaptain Kourtney and Skipper Scott

episode of.title: Kourtney & Khloé Take the Hamptons (TV Series 2014–2015)

6.plot: Khloe and Scott do a podcast, but Scott's loose lips let out a promise that can't be broken. Kourtney believes she's a professional sailor.

7.title: Riding Dirty

episode of.title: Kourtney & Khloé Take the Hamptons (TV Series 2014–2015)

7.plot: When Khloé rekindles her love for horseback riding, Scott and Kourtney make a secret wager on how long she will last and pull out all the stops to push their own agendas. Meanwhile, Kourtney and Kim try to break Kris's cranky mood by cooking her up some romance, and Kris puts a bid on Kim's dream NYC apartment behind her back.

8.title: There's No Smoke Without Fire Island

episode of.title: Kourtney & Khloé Take the Hamptons (TV Series 2014–2015)

8.plot: When Scott is consumed by his negative associations with the Hamptons, he leaves early.

9.title: A House Divided

episode of.title: Kourtney & Khloé Take the Hamptons (TV Series 2014–2015)

9.plot: Kourtney starts fixing up Scott's parents' house, hoping that she can convince him to keep it.

10.title: Best Friends with Benefits

episode of.title: Kourtney & Khloé Take the Hamptons (TV Series 2014–2015)

10.plot: When Khloé enjoys a night of drinking, Kourtney accuses her of putting Scott's sobriety in jeopardy.

imdb.plot outline: Kourtney and Khloé have their work cut out for them as they set out to establish their new pop-up Dash store in The Hamptons while managing the initial struggles of opening their first pop-up store in the trendy and hip beach enclave on Long Island, NY.
